  "detailed_description": "We all know that a clean car drives better. :)<br />\r\n<br />\r\nCar Wash Simulator is racing-simulator game which includes the next jobs: taxi driver & washing sports cars. Over time, the car gets dirty due to dirtyroads. Therefore, you must always keep it clean, because you will not have a request from customers. So, you have to pay close attention at your car.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nGood luck with your work and be carefull on the roads.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nGame Features :<br />\r\n- 10 levels<br />\r\n- 10 supercars<br />\r\n- Dirty roads, pretentious customers<br />\r\n- Gps",
